# Component Rules

Every UI element must be a reusable component. Do NOT duplicate.

Required shared components in `src/components/shared/`:
SearchBar, Sidebar, CollectionRow, PriceBadge, BulkActionBar, EmptyState, PageHeader, CardInspectDialog, CardImage, Modal, QuantityStepper, CollaboratorPresence

Feature pages compose shared components — no inline one-off UI.
